01:05:51,580 --> 01:05:53,104
And you're sure
you can defuse it.

1028
01:05:53,182 --> 01:05:54,615
Yeah. What's more,
l'm the only one.

1029
01:05:58,287 --> 01:05:59,652
No, l need him
to come with me.

1030
01:05:59,722 --> 01:06:00,780
No can do.

1031
01:06:03,059 --> 01:06:04,390
and you defuse the bomb.
How's that?

1032
01:06:04,460 --> 01:06:06,121
You better go.
You've only got nine minutes.

1033
01:06:10,099 --> 01:06:11,657
OK, you both go.

1034
01:06:11,734 --> 01:06:13,031
l'll wait for you down below.

1035
01:06:13,102 --> 01:06:14,865
You gotta come down
sooner or later, huh?

1036
01:06:14,937 --> 01:06:15,904
lf l do the job,
l bet even you...

1037
01:06:15,972 --> 01:06:17,303
will be glad to see a cop's face.

1038
01:06:17,373 --> 01:06:18,431
Hmm.

1039
01:06:48,137 --> 01:06:50,264
What the hell is that?

1040
01:06:50,339 --> 01:06:51,465
A present from Taha.

1041
01:06:53,142 --> 01:06:54,769
Let me handle this.
l love presents.

1042
01:07:46,195 --> 01:07:47,560
Hey, Mongo! You ready now...

1043
01:07:47,630 --> 01:07:48,858
for me to teach you
a thing or two?

1044
01:08:26,669 --> 01:08:28,296
Hey! He's all yours.

1045
01:08:41,283 --> 01:08:43,717
Nice going!
Where did you learn that?

1046
01:08:43,786 --> 01:08:44,946
ln a cookbook or official manual...

1047
01:08:45,021 --> 01:08:46,249
l don't remember.

1048
01:09:13,716 --> 01:09:16,048
lt's all over, Lola, lt's all over.

1049
01:09:18,721 --> 01:09:20,689
No, sorry,
but it's far from over.

1050
01:09:24,126 --> 01:09:25,593
Fuck it,
l can't get through.

1051
01:09:29,398 --> 01:09:31,229
OK, got it.

1052
01:09:31,300 --> 01:09:32,790
Don't worry.
He's an expert at the cuffs.

1053
01:09:32,868 --> 01:09:33,994
He'll get them off you.

1054
01:09:37,740 --> 01:09:39,298
- Hello?
- Captain Tomaso.

1055
01:09:39,375 --> 01:09:41,070
l've got the bomb in front of me.
l need the code.

1056
01:09:41,143 --> 01:09:42,269
Where are you now?

1057
01:09:42,344 --> 01:09:44,107
The bomb's in front of me
with 3 1/2 minutes left.

1058
01:09:44,180 --> 01:09:45,511
Give me the code,
and we'll talk later.

1059
01:09:45,581 --> 01:09:46,775
Where are you? The exact spot.

1060
01:09:46,849 --> 01:09:49,409
On the roof of a building
in Barrio 1 3.

1061
01:09:49,485 --> 01:09:50,611
Do you want
the weather forecast as well?!

1062
01:09:50,686 --> 01:09:52,950
Good work, Tomaso.
We're all very proud of you.

1063
01:09:53,022 --> 01:09:54,284
Thanks, but time's running out.

1064
01:09:54,356 --> 01:09:56,586
9-2-9-3...

1065
01:09:56,659 --> 01:09:58,058
9-2-9-3...

1066
01:09:58,127 --> 01:10:00,493
3-7-0-9-B-1 3.

1067
01:10:00,563 --> 01:10:01,791
7-0-9-B-1 3.

1068
01:10:01,864 --> 01:10:03,491
l'll call you back
if l'm still alive.

1069
01:10:11,841 --> 01:10:13,775
B-1 3? Like Barrio 1 3?

1070
01:10:13,843 --> 01:10:15,538
- Yeah.
- Doesn't it seem strange...

1071
01:10:15,611 --> 01:10:17,010
that the bomb's code is Barrio 1 3...

1072
01:10:17,079 --> 01:10:19,240
92, 93, the two zones we're in?

1073
01:10:19,315 --> 01:10:21,613
Just coincidence.

1074
01:10:21,684 --> 01:10:23,117
Damien, wait! Hold on.

1075
01:10:23,185 --> 01:10:24,277
lf the bomb wasn't scheduled
to come here...

1076
01:10:24,353 --> 01:10:26,014
why the hell does it have
the same number as this barrio?

1077
01:10:26,088 --> 01:10:28,784
Look, whatever it is,
l've got to stop it, OK?

1078
01:10:28,858 --> 01:10:30,450
Damien, listen.
What if it's the reverse?

1079
01:10:30,526 --> 01:10:31,458
The reverse of what?

1080
01:10:31,527 --> 01:10:33,461
You detonate the bomb
with the code instead.

1081
01:10:33,529 --> 01:10:35,156
Why send me, then,
if they wanted the fucking thing...

1082
01:10:35,231 --> 01:10:37,028
to explode in the first place?
Explain that!

1083
01:10:37,099 --> 01:10:38,566
So it blows up right here
where they want...

1084
