Wasn't that what
your boss asked?

1087
01:10:43,072 --> 01:10:44,733
Yeah, but that's
a security measure!

1088
01:10:44,807 --> 01:10:46,001
lt's a trap, Damien,
l'm sure!

1089
01:10:46,075 --> 01:10:47,667
Get off my back
and let me work!

1090
01:10:54,717 --> 01:10:56,309
l've already saved your life once,
so trust me!

1091
01:10:56,385 --> 01:10:58,649
l'm a soldier!
l've got a mission to do!

1092
