was shut down.

1101
01:11:59,782 --> 01:12:01,841
Oh, yeah, the bomb was attacked
by some bad guys, right?

1102
01:12:01,917 --> 01:12:03,817
Yeah.

1103
01:12:03,886 --> 01:12:04,875
That's the story
they told you, huh?

1104
01:12:04,954 --> 01:12:06,046
- Yeah.
- Then tell me why...

1105
01:12:06,121 --> 01:12:07,986
just before we saw the van,
it was intact.

1106
01:12:08,057 --> 01:12:09,354
Where were the signs
of an explosion...

1107
01:12:09,425 --> 01:12:10,915
of a smashed-in door?

1108
01:12:10,993 --> 01:12:11,960
Maybe it was a different one.

1109
01:12:12,027 --> 01:12:13,551
lt was the same,
and you know damn well.

1110
01:12:13,629 --> 01:12:14,721
And once they were sure...

1111
01:12:14,797 --> 01:12:16,264
the bomb was on
the inside of Barrio 1 3...

1112
01:12:16,332 --> 01:12:17,731
and that it wasn't
going anywhere...

1113
01:12:17,800 --> 01:12:19,563
they got their best pit bull
to set it in motion.

1114
01:12:19,635 --> 01:12:21,262
And you really accomplished that mission.

1115
01:12:21,337 --> 01:12:22,395
You stopped Taha
from dumping it...

1116
01:12:22,471 --> 01:12:23,563
so it's all for us.

1117
