1120
01:12:49,698 --> 01:12:51,666
because none of them
were blond with blue eyes!

1121
01:13:25,901 --> 01:13:27,300
Sorry.

1122
01:13:27,369 --> 01:13:28,393
Get off me!

1123
01:13:28,470 --> 01:13:30,529
l prefer dying for my brother's dumb ideas
than for yours.

1124
01:14:02,104 --> 01:14:03,401
lt's over?

1125
01:14:03,472 --> 01:14:05,201
This time it really is over.

1126
01:14:10,179 --> 01:14:11,942
lt's not over.

1127
01:14:28,831 --> 01:14:30,560
l told you that even you...

1128
01:14:30,632 --> 01:14:31,860
would be glad to see my face.

1129
01:14:33,102 --> 01:14:34,592
You got five minutes
to leave here.

1130
01:14:34,670 --> 01:14:36,638
Can l take a souvenir?

1131
01:14:37,906 --> 01:14:39,464
Yeah, be my guest.

1132
01:14:48,450 --> 01:14:50,918
Uh-huh.

1133
01:14:52,421 --> 01:14:54,218
Thank you. Nothing yet.

1134
01:14:54,289 --> 01:14:56,655
Jesus Christ, it's well over an hour
that we've been waiting.

1135
01:14:56,725 --> 01:14:58,056
And if by tonight nothing happens,
then what?

1136
01:14:58,127 --> 01:14:59,526
l've no idea, Corsini.
For Christ's sake...

1137
01:14:59,595 --> 01:15:01,927
it's supposed to explode
and that's that.

1138
01:15:01,997 --> 01:15:03,089
What's going on?

1139
01:15:03,165 --> 01:15:04,393
Sounds like a fight.

1140
01:15:04,466 --> 01:15:05,433
Go and have a look!

1141
01:15:19,481 --> 01:15:20,778
