1158
01:15:52,981 --> 01:15:54,312
end of the summer holidays.

1159
01:15:54,383 --> 01:15:55,975
Practical, eh?
A bomb explodes on the day...

1160
01:15:56,051 --> 01:15:57,712
you know everyone's
around for sure...

1161
01:15:57,786 --> 01:16:00,220
and you get rid of
all the scum in one shot.

1162
01:16:00,289 --> 01:16:01,688
lf l'm mistaken, please stop me.

1163
01:16:01,757 --> 01:16:04,783
Now then, the code.

1164
01:16:04,860 --> 01:16:07,385
