l've been saying that for years!

1229
01:19:07,542 --> 01:19:11,171
Come on, smile.
Lighten up.

1230
01:19:11,246 --> 01:19:12,873
l hope things don't get
messed up on the way...

1231
01:19:12,948 --> 01:19:14,176
and that they keep their promises.

1232
